with a durable suede and canvas upper with padded tongue and lining and Vans signature Waffle Outsole.',3,'2019-06-16 18:05:37','2019-06-19 18:00:07',0,9,1,2),(44,'PLAID ERA Women COLOR-WHITE/TRUE WHITE',1200000,'The Plaid Era combines the Vans classic low top skate shoe with sturdy textile uppers, metal eyelets, padded collars for support and flexibility, and signature rubber waffle outsoles.',3,'2019-06-16 18:08:48','2019-06-19 18:00:19',0,9,1,2),(45,'VANS X HARRY POTTER SK8-HI ZIP COLOR-GRYFFINDOR/MULTI',1000000,'This season, Vans and HARRY POTTER have conjured up a magical collection for witches, wizards, and muggles alike. Featuring sturdy canvas and suede uppers, the Vans x HARRY POTTER Sk8-Hi Zip also includes padded collars for support and flexibility, signature rubber waffle outsoles, custom collaboration details, and a zipper entry at the heel.  Display your GRYFFINDOR™ loyalty in genuine “Off The Wall” style.',3,'2019-06-16 18:12:24','2019-06-19 18:00:31',0,9,2,2),(47,'KIDS CHECKERBOARD OLD SKOOL COLOR-RAINBOW/TRUE WHITE',850000,'The Checkerboard Old Skool, the Vans classic skate shoe and first to bare the iconic sidestripe, is a low top lace-up featuring sturdy suede and canvas uppers with the iconic Vans checkerboard print, re-enforced toecaps to withstand repeated wear, padded collars for support and flexibility, and signature rubber waffle outsoles.\r\n\r\nEach season we offer a range of shoes, apparel and accessories styled with rainbow motifs to enable our global consumers the ability to express their own individuality and creative expression. To celebrate Pride Month 2019, Vans is donating $50,000 to The Trevor Project, the world’s largest suicide prevention and crisis intervention organization for LGBTQ (lesbian, gay, bisexual, transgender, queer and questioning) young people.',3,'2019-06-16 18:20:37','2019-06-19 18:01:05',0,9,3,2),(48,'Chuck Taylor All Star Low Top Optical White',1000000,'WE MAKE THE SHOE. YOU MAKE THE STORIES.\r\nIt started when